These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, sprite, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, almond-milk-polo, cricket, surfing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
2. the person drinking cola is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola   | almond-milk    | coffee    | sprite |
| Sport      | surfing | biathlon | cricket | almond-milk-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, coffee, fanta
There 4 different types of food: grapes, apple, spinach, corn
1. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
3. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person eating apple##6
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | coffee    | soy-milk | fanta    |
| Food       | corn | apple | spinach  | grapes |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, soy-milk, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, software-developer, analyst, firefighter
1. the person drinking coffee is not the designer##6
2. the software-developer is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
3. the analyst is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the software-developer is the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the software-developer##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
7. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
8. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | coffee       | juice  | mirinda  | soy-milk |
| Job        | analyst | firefighter | software-developer | designer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, hamster, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, boat, van
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the van is not the owner of the rabbit##6
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | rabbit | hamster | goat     | chinchilla |
| Transport   | ship     | boat    | scooter | van    |

