.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, almond-milk, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, quad-bike, skateboard, tram
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
4. the person drinking water is not the person driving the tram##6
5. the person driving the subway is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate        | mirinda | almond-milk | water |
| Transport   | tram | subway | quad-bike     | skateboard   |

