.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, comedy, superhero, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: french, chinese, malaysian, japanese
1. the french is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is not the chinese##6
3. the french is on the far right##1
4. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
5. the person watching superhero movies is the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the french##5
7. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
8. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
9. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | superhero    | sports  | documentary   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | japanese | chinese | french |

