.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, horror, animation, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, trance, disco
1. the fan trance is on the left or right of the fan ambient##3
2. the fan trance is not the person watching horror movies##6
3. the person watching mystery movies is the fan house##1
4. the fan ambient is on the left or right of the fan disco##3
5. the fan trance is on the far left##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the fan ambient##1
7. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the fan ambient##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | horror     | animation | mystery |
| Music-Genre   | trance | ambient | disco      | house         |

