.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, cola, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, manager, software-developer, security-guard
1. the accountant is on the left of the manager##1
2. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5
3. the security-guard is on the right of the manager##1
4. the manager is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the accountant is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is not the security-guard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | almond-milk        | cola      | hot-chocolate          |
| Job        | accountant | manager | security-guard | software-developer |

