.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, scientist, electrician, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, taxi, train, boat
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the taxi is not the mechanic##6
3. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the electrician##5
4. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the train##1
6. the person driving the boat is the electrician##1
7. the police-officer is not the person driving the boat##6
8. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | police-officer  | electrician | mechanic    | scientist |
| Transport   | taxi | boat | train | ship  |

