.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, chinchilla, guinea-pig
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, baseball, skiing
1. the person who's sport is parkour is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
6. the person who's sport is cricket is not the owner of the pony##6
7. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | chinchilla | goldfish        | guinea-pig  | pony     |
| Sport   | parkour     | skiing | cricket | baseball |

