.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, video-games, puzzles, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, classical, funk, rock
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the fan classical is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
3. the fan funk is not the person who's hobby is puzzles##6
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the fan rock and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the fan classical is between the fan soul and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles | video-games    | cooking | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | soul         | classical | rock   | funk     |

