4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person eating corn##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is not the person eating pear##6
6. the person eating corn is not the person driving the helicopter##6
7. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the left of the person eating corn##5
8. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
