.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, apricot, peas, nectarine
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, zombie, comedy
1. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the right of the person eating apricot##5
2. the person eating apricot is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
3. the person eating garlic is the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
5. the person eating garlic is between the person eating apricot and the person watching thriller movies##2
6. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | nectarine | apricot      | garlic | peas   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | zombie | comedy   | thriller |

