.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure, western, family
1. the person watching western movies is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
2. the person watching western movies is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person watching family movies is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk       | tea | milk     | iced-tea     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | western       | family | adventure |

