.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, camping, baking, collecting
4 different pets are kept: goat, cat, guinea-pig, hedgehog
1. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
2. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is camping##2
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | camping | baking | writing | collecting |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | cat      | goat  | hedgehog       |

