4. the person driving the car is not the person drinking cola##6
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
6. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | cola | tea | juice      | soy-milk   |
| Transport   | ship  | helicopter   | bus | car |

 